{"tid":1367794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警政內戰唔好咁開心住，最緊要拉低鄧柄強","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T08:47:34.000Z","uid":188176,"like":123,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f215a0f659a79232b0cfd33aaffbaa939bfbec","tid":1367794,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"唔可以比隻黑犬做到一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b525e990f1d2995d6aa2dfe9f2796cf09e7245","tid":1367794,"uid":39205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"聽日個遊行係「反黑遊行」呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367790</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a05d12ed7385245520c594b22ff925b6dbbbfd91","tid":1367794,"uid":44870,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:56:44.000Z","msg":"2佬對外勾結牛屎佬, 對內安撫唔住班手足, 庸碌無能"},{"pid":"5227c55a54e8cb461167036c0a251f6853386f24","tid":1367794,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f68010c6a8a8b50be51437034b81b6d4ac55bc","tid":1367794,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"bump<br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔通吹風吹到咁行就係出呢招？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂攞正牌入嚟香港平亂<br />\n大家醒水，睇嚟有勢力仲想翻盤 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府文人高層都被下層武官批鬥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 武官就不斷（／被有心人士）推高水溫<br />\n<br />\n學另外兩位巴打話齋，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張建宗文官高層被下層武官插，都係<strong><ins>劇本之一</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n「黑警宣布獨立並成立軍政府<br />\n香港特別行政區政府即時失效<br />\n另一邊箱， 香港人民成立臨時獨立政府及組成反抗軍<br />\n中國暗幫軍政府，美國援助反抗勢力<br />\n地區戰爆發<br />\n擦槍走火演變成WW3<br />\n<br />\n時代雜誌表示，送綠帽俾陳同佳果位人兄成為21世紀最有影響力風雲人物首位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">劇本<br />\n黑警 威脅 政府<br />\n政府 call 老解<br />\n老解 vs 黑警+白衣人<br />\n一國一制正式落實</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c577f65c1e7be82ebeb4c127517b48ea9392ae93","tid":1367794,"uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a05d12ed7385245520c594b22ff925b6dbbbfd91","tid":1367794,"uid":44870,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:56:44.000Z","msg":"2佬對外勾結牛屎佬, 對內安撫唔住班手足, 庸碌無能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:57:31.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8280d78255fdb3f015b4e7706d730d8ef906e4","tid":1367794,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d625df16856e30c9fd276d527a450c383d15a9","tid":1367794,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a9fbe9d4402c7cf38f9520475b54aba08186d1","tid":1367794,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9a038a297ce7ff8b272fb82347ac8e96725e77","tid":1367794,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r